---
import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="Learn about Chill Dogs — our mission to help dog parents find the best gear, gifts, and party ideas for their four-legged family members.">
  <section class="about container">
    <div class="prose">
      <h1>About Chill Dogs</h1>
      <p>
        Welcome to Chill Dogs — a curated corner of the internet for dog parents who believe their pups deserve the good life.
      </p>
      <p>
        We started Chill Dogs because we know the feeling: you want to throw the perfect birthday party for your dog, find a gift that actually holds up to enthusiastic chewing, or discover gear that matches your lifestyle. But with thousands of options out there, finding the right stuff is overwhelming.
      </p>
      <p>
        That's where we come in. We research, test, and review products so you don't have to. Every recommendation on this site is something we'd genuinely pick for our own dogs. No filler, no fluff — just honest picks for happy pups.
      </p>

      <h2>What We Cover</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Party Ideas</strong> — Everything you need to throw an unforgettable dog birthday party or celebration</li>
        <li><strong>Gift Guides</strong> — Thoughtfully curated gifts for dogs and the people who love them</li>
        <li><strong>Luxury & Gear</strong> — Premium products for dogs with refined taste</li>
        <li><strong>Blog</strong> — Tips, stories, and insights from the chill dog lifestyle</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Our Promise</h2>
      <p>
        Every product we recommend has been carefully researched. We use affiliate links to keep this site running — that means if you purchase something through our links, we may earn a small commission at no additional cost to you. This never influences our recommendations. Your trust matters more than any commission.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about {
    padding-top: var(--space-3xl);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-4xl);
  }

  .about h1 {
    font-size: var(--text-4xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }
</style>
